					<h1>Akamai Youth</h1>
					<p class="major">Supporting Hawaiʻi’s youth and families through technology, mentorship, and opportunity.</p>
					<p>Akamai Youth is a Hawaiʻi based nonprofit. Our focus is simple. We support youth with limited access to technology through hands on learning, caring mentors, and community support that feels local and real.</p>
					<ul class="actions stacked">
