			<section class="spotlight style1 orient-right content-align-left image-position-center onscroll-image-fade-in" id="youth">
				<div class="content">
					<h2>For youth and families</h2>
					<p>We’re here for keiki and ʻohana. Technology moves fast, and not every family has the same time, access, or support. Akamai Youth helps bridge that gap in a way that feels welcoming. No judgment, no pressure, and no assumptions.</p>
					<p><strong>What families can expect</strong></p>
					<ul>
						<li>Hands on learning that builds confidence and curiosity</li>
						<li>Positive mentorship and a safe place to ask questions and grow</li>
						<li>Practical technology skills that translate to school, work, and everyday life</li>
					</ul>
					<ul class="actions stacked">
						<li><a href="#programs" class="button">See what we do</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
